        "class": "ital",
        "text": "modus operandi",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " of the miracle reminds us of that of the paralytic in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Matthew 9:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and the cripple at Bethesda in ",
        "children": []
